text.tspan: Acthouggas is by far one of our most loyal and dedicated members.
He freed manachrei and usually spies on Donk for us before Solomon
showed up and sort of took it on naturally. And there has been recent
rumors of Acthouggas in a relationship with Nile Parkas from Donk.
Recently he came back with a greenish tinge. He said he awakened.
I don't know what that means.
